data.description: Wow, Wow, Wow...this DiVosta 2/2 Capri with 2 Car Garage is a show stopper. Very well taken care of, overlooking the private  pool area and backing up to preserve. The minute you walk in... this place has you captured with its loving decorations, upgraded kitchen drawers that pull out and shiplap style walls...just to name a few things. The AC is 2021, H2O heater 2022 and washer & dryer 2021. Lost Lake Golf Club is a semi-private, Jim and Tom Fazio designed, 18-hole, Championship Golf Course with optional social membership. This great location is close to the beach, marina's, shopping and Restaurants. This villa should definitely be on your list to see if you are in the market for a new or second home.
